SUMMARY:PUNCHLINE MONDAYS (Free Comedy Show Hosted & Curated by Jeff Joe)
DTSTAMP:20260627T134356Z
DTSTART:20260914T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:\nPunchline Mondays is the BEST weekly stand-up comedy show you
	’ll find in the city of Houston! The show is FREE - So the laughs are on u
	s! Guaranteed the BEST way to start off your week. Come get these laughs e
